<tr><td>台股待發放</td><td style="color:#FF9800;font-weight:bold">+{div_pending:,.0f} 元</td><td>已除息尚未入帳（Yahoo動態）</td></tr>
<tr><td>美股實收</td><td style="color:#4CAF50;font-weight:bold">+USD {us_dividend_total:.2f}</td><td>≈ TWD {us_dividend_ntwd:,.0f}（已扣30%預扣稅）</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f5f5f5;font-weight:bold"><td>合計實收</td><td style="color:#2e7d32">≈ {div_confirmed+us_dividend_ntwd:,.0f} 元</td><td>台股+美股</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#fff9e6"><td>總累計</td><td style="color:#2e7d32;font-weight:bold">{total_with_fx_sign}{total_with_fx:,.0f} 元</td><td>含市值+美股+匯差（成本匯率 28.5）</td></tr>
</table>
